<p>Welcome to {{ dialog.name }}</p>

<p>This is the form to fill in to join:</p>

<form action="/front/dialogjoin" method="post">
<input type="hidden" name="group_id" value="{{ group.id }}">      
<input type="hidden" name="dialog_id" value="{{ @dialog.id }}">	
<table style="background-color:#fff;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto;width:700px">    
<tr><td>Subject</td><td><input type="text" name="subject" value="{{ subject }}" size="48" style="width:600px"></td></tr>
<tr><td>Message</td><td><textarea name="message" class="editor" cols="80" rows="6" style="width:600px;height:200px">{% if message == empty %}Dear Friends,{% else %}{{ message }}{% endif %}
</textarea></td></tr>  
{% for m in meta %}
<tr><td>{{ m.name }}</td><td><select name="meta_{{ m.id }}">{% for node in m.nodes %}<option value="{{ node.id }}"{% if node.id == m.val %} selected="selected"{% endif %}>{{ node.name }}</option>{% endfor %}</select></td></tr>
{% endfor %}
<tr><td>*Country of Residence</td><td><select name="country_code"><option value="">* choose *</option>{% for country in countries %}<option value="{{ country.iso }}"{% if country.iso == country_code %} selected="selected"{% endif %}>{{ country.name }}</option>{% endfor %}</select></td></tr>
<tr><td>*Your Name</td><td><input type="text" name="name" value="{{ name }}" size="30" style="width:200px"></td></tr>    
<tr><td>*E-mail</td><td><input type="text" name="email" value="{{ email }}" size="30" style="width:200px"></td></tr>    
</table>
<input type="submit" value="Register!">    
</form>

<p>A confirmation email will be sent. Be sure to respond to that email. Your message cannot be posted in the discussion until you have confirmed your registration.</p>

<p>When you have confirmed, you will be automatically taken to the message list to vote on your own message and those written by others. It is OK to vote on your own message. Once your message receives its first rating, you will no longer be able to make changes in it. </p>

<p>If you have questions, please contact the discussion coordinator, Roger Eaton, at <a href="mailto:rogerweaton@gmail.com">rogerweaton@gmail.com</a>.</p>